Revision history for Sys-Monitor-Lite

0.07  2025-12-13
    - Add Prometheus text exposition output with --prefix/--labels helpers
      and optional timestamps.

0.06  2025-12-13
    - Bump version for inode and mount monitoring enhancements.

0.05  2025-12-13
    - Add lightweight process metric with --top/--watch CLI helpers and
      basic CPU/RSS sampling from /proc.

0.04  2025-12-13
    - Add Nagios-style threshold parsing helpers and --check/--warn/--crit
      CLI switches that return compact status output with exit codes.

0.03  2025-12-13
    - Add YAML output support for the module and CLI.

0.02  2025-10-22
    - Add disk I/O metrics collector and documentation updates.

0.01  2025-10-19
    - Initial release to CPAN.
